description:
This week, Joe and Mama Fran have a special guest on, tour manager Jeff! They watch an amazingly awful s**t show on the water called Below Deck Sailing Yacht! Jeff brings his reality TV passion to the show and Mama Fran learns a little bit about chlamydia!
